NAME            CALMIRA
DESCRIPTION     'Calmira - Windows 3.1 Shell Replacement'
EXETYPE         WINDOWS
STUB            'WINSTUB.EXE'

CODE            PRELOAD MOVEABLE DISCARDABLE
DATA            PRELOAD MOVEABLE MULTIPLE
HEAPSIZE        4096
STACKSIZE       16384
